snippet.title: Peacequarium New Graphics - The aquarium simulator you can place anywhere on your screen
snippet.description:
An idle aquarium simulator you can resize and keep anywhere on your screen while you do other things. Buy, feed, and grow your fish to earn money. Buy cool upgrades and complete your collection of rare, epic and legendary fish! Wishlist and sign up for the playtest!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3109830/Peacequarium/
